        "found": true,
        "localization": {
          "name": "Moonlight Thief",
          "description": "This unit cannot be poisoned or burned.\n\nWhenever an enemy on the battlefield is defeated or sacrificed by any source, this unit will immediately have its TU reduced to 0. Then this effect cannot trigger again until 50TU advances.\n\nEach time this unit takes damage from an attack and survives until after the end of the turn, this unit will be Purified. This unit has 35% damage reduction from attacks. This unit has 70% damage reduction from attacks instead if this unit has any Ward (e.g. a Sleep Ward)"
        }
      },
      "EnteringTheBattlefieldPassiveALupinRegularBoss": {
        "id": "EnteringTheBattlefieldPassiveALupinRegularBoss",
        "found": true,
        "localization": {
          "name": "Two Steps Ahead",
          "description": "This unit cannot be sent to the reinforcements from the battlefield.\n\nIf this unit would be defeated by an enemy attack or a status effect while having more than 1 HP, it instead survives with 1 HP.\n\nThis unit enters battle with a Sleep Ward, Stun Ward and Super Stealth.\n\nSuper Stealthed units ignore enemy attacks that would damage more than 1 target. Super Stealth will be removed after ignoring 3 enemy attacks since applying, and can be overwritten by other status effects, except normal Stealth. Damage will not remove Super Stealth."
        }
      }
